  "description": "A close-up view of a rocky stream bed with water flowing over and around various sized rocks. The rocks are predominantly grey, brown, and reddish in color, creating a textured and uneven landscape. Patches of vibrant green vegetation, primarily low-lying plants and grasses, grow amongst and around the rocks, adding a touch of life and color to the scene. The water appears clear and reflects some of the surrounding light. The background is a dense collection of green foliage, suggesting a forest or wooded area.",
